| ------------------- | ----------------------- | ------------------------------------------ |
| Hoisting            | âœ… Memory Creation Phase | `var`, `let`, `const`, functions           |
| Lexical Environment | âœ… Memory Creation Phase | Holds variable/function declarations       |
